# Salesforce Opportunity Risk Assessment Automation

## Overview
Built a Salesforce Record-Triggered Flow that automatically identifies high-risk sales opportunities.

## Business Rule
- Discount > 20%
- AI Risk Score = High
- Approval Required = True

## Components Used
- Opportunity Object
- Custom Fields
- Salesforce Flow
- Decision Element
- Update Records Element

## Result
When a sales opportunity exceeds the discount threshold, Salesforce automatically flags it as high risk and requires approval.
